    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> October 15, 2025</p>

    <p>Calibi Sync (“we,” “our,” or “us”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use the Calibi Sync mobile application (“App”) and related services. By using Calibi Sync, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree, please discontinue use of the App.</p>

    <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>We collect only the information needed to provide and improve Calibi Sync’s features.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> email, display name, height, weight, birthday, and wellness goals.</li>
      <li><strong>Cycle &amp; Health Data:</strong> menstrual cycle details, symptoms, intimate days, workouts, meals, journal entries, and progress photos — all protected through Supabase encryption.</li>
      <li><strong>Device &amp; Usage Data:</strong> anonymized device info, app version, and crash logs to improve stability.</li>
      <li><strong>Payment Data:</strong> processed securely through RevenueCat / App Store. We do not store payment card details.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Provide personalized insights and core features</li>
      <li>Sync your logs securely across sessions</li>
      <li>Analyze app performance and fix bugs</li>
      <li>Send optional notifications</li>
      <li>Manage subscriptions via RevenueCat</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We <strong>never sell or rent</strong> your personal information.</p>

    <h3>3. Data Storage &amp; Security</h3>
    <p>Your data is securely stored in <strong>Supabase</strong>, encrypted in transit and at rest. Supabase complies with SOC 2 and ISO 27001. While we take reasonable measures, no system is 100% secure.</p>

    <h3>4. Sharing &amp; Third-Party Access</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — secure database, authentication, and file storage.</li>
      <li><strong>RevenueCat</strong> — subscription verification and billing.</li>
      <li><strong>Anonymous analytics</strong> — performance metrics only.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do <strong>not</strong> share personally identifiable health data with advertisers.</p>

    <h3>5. Your Rights &amp; Controls</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>View &amp; Edit:</strong> update profile info anytime.</li>
      <li><strong>Delete Account:</strong> permanently remove your data (Storage, Database, Auth).</li>
      <li><strong>Export or Request Data:</strong> email <a href="mailto:support@calibisync.com">support@calibisync.com</a>.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>6. Data Retention</h3>
    <p>Data is kept only while your account is active. Once deleted, all entries and files are permanently removed.</p>

    <h3>7. Children’s Privacy</h3>
    <p>Calibi Sync is not intended for users under 13 (or 16 where required by law). We do not knowingly collect data from minors.</p>

    <h3>8. International Data Transfers</h3>
    <p>Your data may be processed and stored in the U.S. or other regions where Supabase operates. By using Calibi Sync, you consent to these transfers.</p>

    <h3>9. Wellness Disclaimer</h3>
    <p>Calibi Sync provides holistic wellness insights only. It is <strong>not medical advice</strong> and does not replace professional diagnosis or treatment. Always consult your healthcare provider for medical concerns.</p>

    <h3>10. Changes</h3>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. The latest version with its effective date will always appear here and in the App.</p>

    <h3>11. Contact</h3>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@calibisync.com">support@calibisync.com</a></p>
